      "content": "hey, looking at the spec sheet for those industrial drills from apex. we're thinking about a fleet order for the new warehouse site, maybe 50+ units. but i need to be sure about the runtime. our shifts are long. can these actually handle a full 24-hour cycle of heavy use without needing a charge mid-shift? if they can, we can sign today.",
