      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds good on paper, but i've heard some mixed things about the heavy-duty battery life on previous models. Are you absolutely sure about the 24-hour claim for high-intensity drilling? If we find out mid-operation that they die after 16 or 18 hours, it's going to be a huge problem for our logistics and the contract will be void. I need a firm confirmation.",
